{"tid":428136,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人為咗反曹星如竟然走去踩低「運動員」呢個職業","createTime":"2017-10-07T21:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-08T05:25:03.000Z","uid":146924,"like":6,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"31b064da52d3c65fc9fc452351923b1cf977a7fa","tid":428136,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T21:36:38.000Z","msg":"「運動員」算唔算係香港種姓制度嘅最高階層?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/427943/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/427943/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n我有冇睇錯？為咗反一個拳手竟然走去踩低「運動員」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁你哋當初有咩資格笑梁振英講體育界對香港冇經濟貢獻？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 原來你哋打從心底裏面都有同樣嘅想法<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/08/053407_760ba6b5963a3e3514671a9b5a45b92e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F08%2F053407_760ba6b5963a3e3514671a9b5a45b92e.jpg&h=96f27201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n引述返當時嘅媒體：<br />\n運動員付出了無數日子的汗水及努力，在國際賽事上取得佳績，為本港增光，這又如何計 ?況且就算某些人只向錢看，若說體育沒有經濟貢獻，也一樣說不過去。 <br />\n李慧詩稱，無論宗教和體育，在社會上都處於一個重要的地位，並影響社會的發展，更反問「關乎的何止是經濟貢獻」。"},{"pid":"f593c540285330c3d2f00f187f8d7c9c0686f809","tid":428136,"uid":99627,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T22:11:01.000Z","msg":"連登仔不嬲都戇鳩"},{"pid":"81140009e9486ccff835f2d9cda83a341fac2e1e","tid":428136,"uid":37713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T23:01:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>連登仔不嬲都戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n駁唔到"},{"pid":"e576e2f66c457aea616516ba5617b302102e66fd","tid":428136,"uid":69886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-07T23:05:51.000Z","msg":"不嬲我都覺得唔應該投放咁多資源落運動發展 香港咁撚多窮人佢唔幫?"},{"pid":"e5f0961baafd9c54000837f9ba659fdee14fd414","tid":428136,"uid":146924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-08T00:42:21.000Z","msg"